sentences: Tom Lundén  (born March 16, 1950) is a Danish composer and music producer.
Lunden was the leader and keyboardist of the flower power rock band Bifrost.
His two top hits with Bifrost were Hej Maria (Hello, Maria) and Det er morgen ("It's Morning").
Lundén also wrote the 1976 protest song I kan ikke slå os ihjel (English: "You cannot kill us") as an anthem for the revolutionary hippie commune of Christiania.
